lead_paragraph: The initial public offering would have spun off JBS’s Brazilian pork, poultry and food operations and raised up to 3.5 billion reais ($1.2 billion).

headline.main: I.P.O. Plans Withdrawn for Spinoff of JBS, World’s Largest Meatpacker

snippet: The initial public offering would have spun off JBS’s Brazilian pork, poultry and food operations and raised up to 3.5 billion reais ($1.2 billion).
